ji\" />」"},{"pid":"1ddffcfa274dae51ff4ef5ffdbc80a2a8119bfec","tid":2413493,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:00:35.000Z","msg":"癲雞成日揾癲佬幫佢凶人，前後進行包夾，癲佬仲會推人心口。"},{"pid":"5095f81e605934fb8b9f24b035d48a01745bd842","tid":2413493,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:03:10.000Z","msg":"癲雞同癲佬最中意夾埋揾單獨活動嘅人出手。"},{"pid":"2dcccfb8c7d18fc73b81f413b5e0013f3ab9c2e4","tid":2413493,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"再加上癲婆，形成鐵三角劈友陣法。"},{"pid":"0c7db66f4560236cd73a499050283f9c5618958b","tid":2413493,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:07:09.000Z","msg":"三人成虎，走唔甩就死得，死得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f287684c083f23e4a54084c295e96fc84d40f66","tid":2413493,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T18:10:02.000Z","msg":"三人成虎"},{"pid":"1175ed7140f4642428b36fa879790d711f874b0f","tid":2413493,"uid":184509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T00:39:54.000Z","msg":"你up乜鳩??????????????????????????"},{"pid":"631d48c14574e1d9da5da4e8f914e1b1184598ff","tid":2413493,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1175ed7140f4642428b36fa879790d711f874b0f","tid":2413493,"uid":184509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T00:39:54.000Z","msg":"你up乜鳩??????????????????????????"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"癲雞係一個college職員，佢中意搞單獨活動嘅毒llll學生，搞到佢死或者走為止，唔會放手。癲雞後面個癲佬係佢手下，平時會聽癲雞指揮幫手去凶單獨嘅毒lllll學生。有一次仲打個入醫院訓左好多日。"},{"pid":"3b8421584d6cca82a5735a00e2af124abb9a416c","tid":2413493,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1175ed7140f4642428b36fa879790d711f874b0f","tid":2413493,"uid":184509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-1